# Uploads Directory

This directory is used for storing uploaded files.

## Important

- Files in this directory are gitignored (except this README)
- Ensure proper file permissions in production
- Implement file size limits and validation
- Consider using cloud storage (AWS S3, Google Cloud Storage) for production

## Security

- Never store sensitive files without encryption
- Implement virus scanning for uploaded files
- Validate file types before saving
- Use unique filenames to prevent conflicts

## Cleanup

Implement automated cleanup for:
- Temporary files
- Orphaned uploads
- Files from deleted records
